title: Suite Precure♪ Movie: Torimodose! Kokoro ga Tsunagu Kiseki no Melody♪
synopsis: After Cure Muse's mission of restoring her father's kind heart was accomplished, Ako and Mephisto decided to return to Major Land together. Suddenly, a howling noise rang through the city, and when it died down, all music was gone. Ako and Mephisto tried to establish contact with Major Land, but could not get a response.
